      "para_id": "Q000933.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ig-alima , his master , Urabba , the grand vizier , child of Utukam , the overseer , dedicated this ( mace ) for the well-being of Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , and also for his own well-being ."
    }
